{"tid":1323141,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"6.21 投奔初夏 政總夏日沙灘節！！！","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T09:05:04.000Z","uid":200042,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dd415aa736046ee484aa1e84b132b9d79371c5","tid":1323141,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:56:06.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">炎炎夏日將至，一眾市民都應投奔初夏，玩一眾港人愛玩的沙灘運動!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n第一屆全民初夏運動會於金鐘舉行，屆時大家可帶備名種沙灘玩具，到場慶祝<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 飛碟</span><br />\n<br />\n受美國隊長同垃圾會君妖大隊長所啟發，大家可帶備飛碟，由於飛碟易於控制，加上價錢相宜，適合遠距離攻擊，而感覺亦比磚頭好，所以強烈建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 沙灘排球</span><br />\n<br />\n人妖打排球所描畫既殺波相信深入民心，希望一眾運動巴打帶排球於到時大大力殺落對家，強身健體<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 浮棒</span><br />\n<br />\n大大支浮棒可臨場殺敵，軟身有助吸收攻擊，亦能遠距離對對家做成滋擾，顔色亦有助辨認自己人<br />\n<br />\n都係突然諗到，有建議大家可再講講"},{"pid":"ff7ee5e2002169b2a56d010760f1944b5e574f1a","tid":1323141,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b6debe356032fd0af9342a8891cf9e530fb42745","tid":1323141,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22304432af21095da9bb489971a7c43564e3f6f9","tid":1323141,"uid":215700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:56:52.000Z","msg":"係咪打錯日子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137a5bd29531da3f7f56287745db9d0cf7bfb010","tid":1323141,"uid":272565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"21/7?"},{"pid":"c1440aa746ed7447363611f7e048ec12d42dae37","tid":1323141,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"621<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca05ff